description: Santa's Route - You can check out Santa's route based on this information from Travel by GPS. You can E-mail Travel by GPS (http://earth.google.com/userguide/v4/ug_sharingplacedata.html#emailplace)a placemark from Google Earth for the location of your house, and they will add your house to the route.
